display="inline"><![CDATA[1\leq \nu \leq  n]]></fr:tex> such that <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mu \neq \nu ]]></fr:tex></fr:li>
<fr:li>Swapping two rows: <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\det (\mathbf {I}+\mathbf {E}_{\mu ,\nu }+\mathbf {E}_{\nu ,\mu }-\mathbf {E}_{\mu ,\mu }-\mathbf {E}_{\nu ,\nu })=(-1)^{\mu -\nu }]]></fr:tex></fr:li>
<fr:li><fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\det (\mathbf {I}+r\mathbf {E}_{\mu ,\mu })=1+r]]></fr:tex> for any <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[r]]></fr:tex></fr:li></fr:ol><fr:p>The first and third claim follows immediately from the fact that the <fr:link
