display="inline"><![CDATA[V]]></fr:tex>. Let <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[L\colon  V\to  V]]></fr:tex> be a linear operator of <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[V]]></fr:tex>. Suppose <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[M(L)=(a_{ij})]]></fr:tex> is the matrix of <fr:tex
