<fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[\det (L)=\sum _{\pi \in  S_{n}}\mathop {\mathrm {sgn}}\nolimits (\pi )a_{1,\pi (1)}a_{2,\pi (2)}(…)a_{n,\pi (n)}]]></fr:tex>
where the sum is taken over all <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[n!]]></fr:tex> permutations.</fr:p><fr:p>Compare this to the <fr:link
type="local"
