display="inline"><![CDATA[C]]></fr:tex>, then <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[[L]_{C}=M^{B}_{C}[L]_{B}M^{C}_{B}]]></fr:tex> and the determinant of both  sides are the same since <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[M^{B}_{C}=(M^{C}_{B})^{-1}]]></fr:tex>, <fr:link
type="local"
href="matrix-001Z.xml"
